338
00:20:41.490 --> 00:20:43.867 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Just hurry and find one!

339
00:20:45.410 --> 00:20:47.704 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>Hey, Hachi.</i>

340
00:20:48.580 --> 00:20:51.875 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>Humans are such pathetic creatures.</i>

341
00:20:51.959 --> 00:20:54.294 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
